				}
			]
		},
		{
			"type": "paragraph",
			"children": [
				{
					"type": "text",
					"text": "You can easily reach the islands by boat from Lombok (the cheapest option) or from Bali via Padangbai or Amed. There is no public ferry from Bali to the Gili Islands, so it’s impossible to find a low-cost option. The only option is private speedboats. You can buy a ticket from one of the vendors in the port before 9 AM, and you can haggle over the price. To travel between the individual islands, you can either take a private boat (which is quite expensive considering the distance) or buy a ticket at the port office for the public ferry just before departure. This is the cheapest option and allows you to reach any of the islands or even Lombok."
				}
			]
		},
